  - Implement /files: POST to save/update files; GET to read; GET /files/list to enumerate.
  - Implement /stt: stub or real integration (optional); return transcription result.
  - Implement /tts: synthesize_text to audio (use gTTS or similar); return base64 audio data.
  - Session management: remember recent messages for context continuity, with an optional timeout/cleanup.
  - Logging and error handling.
