Phase 6 — Delivery and review
Subgoal 6.1: Produce the final README with all sections filled
- Objective: Compile all the planning, implementation notes, and usage instructions into a comprehensive README.
- Rationale: The user-facing guide is the ultimate deliverable.
- Deliverables: Final README.md that includes architecture, setup steps, usage, how the summary is generated, and how to extend the pipeline.
