- Why it matters: ensures quality gates and reproducible builds from day one.

Subgoal 7: Module-by-module rewrite plan (the core plan)
- What to do: For each file/module, define how you’ll rewrite it.
- For each module/file include:
  - Purpose, inputs, outputs, side effects.
