High-level goals
- Build a production-ready Unity project that hosts a realistic anime-style female streamer character.
- Real-time, multilingual (English/French) dialogue driven by an AI backend with memory and learning hooks.
- Real-time facial (mouth/eye) and body animations driven by speech and emotion.
- Twitch and Discord integration for chat and voice; streaming metadata/events linked to OBS-like overlays.
