Phase 0: Project scaffolding and tooling (foundation)
Subgoals
- Set up Unity project
  - Create a clean Unity LTS project (latest LTS). Enable newer input system; enable Addressables if you plan to use them.
  - Create directory structure: Assets/Scripts, Assets/Models, Assets/Animations, Assets/Audio, Assets/Prefabs, Packages, etc.
  - Add a README/INSTRUCTIONS.txt at project root with build/run steps and extension guidelines.
- Establish source control and CI basics
  - Initialize Git; add .gitignore for Unity; consider a small GitHub Actions workflow for automated builds (Windows/Mac) if desired.
- Create a basic runtime scaffold
