- Decide default neutral pose and safe animation blending to avoid jitter.

Subgoal 4: AI personality, memory, and language model integration plan
What you’ll do
- Define the AI persona behavior model:
  - Funny, silly, a little mischievous; teaches life lessons; highly emotional and expressive.
  - Bilingual capability: English and French, with language switching based on context.
  - Memory: remember past interactions, topics, and viewer behaviors.
  - Adapt over time from ongoing interactions.
- Decide on the external AI loop:
  - Use an API-based language model (GPT-5-nano or equivalent) for text generation.
  - Use a memory store (in-memory + lightweight persistent store) to retain context per session/viewer.
