- `obs_controller.py` — uses OBS WebSocket to switch scenes, control audio routing, toggle virtual cam, and to monitor stream health.
- `safety_filter.py` — profanity filter, disallowed topics, and a configurable refusal policy. Integrate pre-response and post-response checks.
- `utils/audio_utils.py` — audio pipeline helpers (pitch/formant shift, reverb, EQ) using `pydub` or `sox` subprocess calls.
- `tests/` — unit and integration tests for all pure-Python modules.

